headline: Franklin Templeton files for Solana ETF a day after requesting XRP ETF
summary: Franklin Templeton has requested the U.S. SEC to list a Solana ETF. If approved, it would become the largest asset manager to launch a Solana ETF

headline: Franklin Templeton Files for XRP ETF as Cryptocurrency Adoption Grows Among Asset Managers
summary: Franklin Templeton has filed for an exchange-traded fund (ETF) that will track the spot price of XRP, one of the leading cryptocurrencies.
